**Note:** This configuration creates a complete working setup including VPC resources required by OpenSearch Serverless collections. Update subnet CIDRs, security group rules, and index mappings as needed for your specific use case. The Firehose stream delivers data to the `firehose-index` in the OpenSearch Serverless collection.

