  skip_final_snapshot = true
}
```

**Notes:**
- Replace `subnet-12345678`, `subnet-87654321`, `vpc-12345678` with your actual VPC/subnet IDs
- Update the S3 bucket ARN in the IAM policy (`your-s3-bucket`)
- Adjust CIDR blocks in security group as needed
- Change region, node type, and other parameters based on your requirements
- The IAM role includes example S3 permissions - modify as needed for your use case

