**Note:** Create a `lambda.js` file in the same directory as your Terraform configuration with a sample export like:

```javascript
exports.handler = async (event) => {
  console.log('Hello from Lambda!');
  return {
    statusCode: 200,
    body: JSON.stringify('Hello, World!'),
  };
};
```

