  ingress {
    from_port   = 443
    to_port     = 443
    protocol    = "tcp"
    cidr_blocks = ["0.0.0.0/0"]
  }

  egress {
    from_port   = 0
    to_port     = 0
    protocol    = "-1"
    cidr_blocks = ["0.0.0.0/0"]
  }
}
```

**Note:** This configuration includes prerequisite resources (SageMaker Domain, IAM Role, VPC, Security Group) required for creating a SageMaker User Profile. Adjust region, names, VPC settings, and IAM policies according to your environment. The `domain_id` must exist before creating the user profile.

