This configuration creates:
- A VPC with public (10.0.1.0/24) and private (10.0.2.0/24) subnets
- Internet Gateway and public route table for internet access
- Security group allowing SSH (22) and HTTP (80) access
- Launch template using the latest Amazon Linux 2 AMI with t3.medium instances
- EC2 Fleet with 5 On-Demand + 4 Spot instances (total 9) across both subnets
- User data to install and start Apache web server
- Basic outputs for reference

