**Note:** This configuration creates a complete MSK cluster with VPC, subnets, security groups, and CloudWatch Logs integration. The IAM role grants MSK permission to write broker logs to the specified CloudWatch Log Group. Apply with `terraform init`, `terraform plan`, and `terraform apply`.

