**Note:** Amazon MSK Serverless clusters are managed automatically by AWS and do not require explicit broker node configuration (the "three broker nodes" is handled internally by AWS). The configuration above provisions a production-ready MSK Serverless cluster with IAM authentication across 3 AZs. Apply with `terraform init && terraform apply`.

