**Usage:**
```hcl
# Example terraform.tfvars
subnet_id         = "subnet-0123456789abcdef0"
eip_allocation_id = "eipalloc-0123456789abcdef0"
```

This configuration creates a publicly accessible NAT Gateway in the specified subnet using the provided EIP allocation ID. The NAT Gateway enables outbound internet access for instances in private subnets while keeping inbound traffic blocked.

