**Note:** The Network ACL is created and attached to the VPC. No subnets were specified in the request, so `subnet_ids` is empty (ACL applies to all subnets in the VPC by default). Ephemeral ports rule added for practical return traffic. Default deny-all rules are handled automatically by AWS.

